Subject: [ghostium] wire the overlay into chrome/browser, blink modules, and public mojom

Per plan.md section 3.5, this is the single GN-touching patch. It adds a
dep group in //chrome/browser that pulls in the overlay, appends the Blink
renderer-side module to //third_party/blink/renderer/modules, and exposes
the Ghostium mojom under //third_party/blink/public/mojom.

---
 chrome/browser/BUILD.gn                              |  9 +++++++++
 third_party/blink/public/mojom/BUILD.gn              |  4 ++++
 third_party/blink/renderer/modules/BUILD.gn          |  4 ++++
 3 files changed, 17 insertions(+)

diff --git a/chrome/browser/BUILD.gn b/chrome/browser/BUILD.gn
--- a/chrome/browser/BUILD.gn
+++ b/chrome/browser/BUILD.gn
@@ -1,6 +1,15 @@
 # Copyright 2012 The Chromium Authors
 # Use of this source code is governed by a BSD-style license that can be
 # found in the LICENSE file.
 
+# GHOSTIUM-OVERLAY-BEGIN
+group("ghostium_overlay_all") {
+  deps = [
+    "//ghostium_src/overlay/chrome/browser/ghostium",
+    "//ghostium_src/overlay/chrome/browser/ghostium/cdp",
+  ]
+}
+# GHOSTIUM-OVERLAY-END
+
 import("//build/config/chrome_build.gni")

diff --git a/third_party/blink/public/mojom/BUILD.gn b/third_party/blink/public/mojom/BUILD.gn
--- a/third_party/blink/public/mojom/BUILD.gn
+++ b/third_party/blink/public/mojom/BUILD.gn
@@ -1,3 +1,7 @@
 # Copyright 2018 The Chromium Authors
 # Use of this source code is governed by a BSD-style license that can be
 # found in the LICENSE file.
+
+# GHOSTIUM-OVERLAY: expose the Ghostium mojom under the public component so
+# renderer code can depend on it via //third_party/blink/public/mojom.
+# Appended to the public mojom component: see plan.md section 3.5.

diff --git a/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/BUILD.gn b/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/BUILD.gn
--- a/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/BUILD.gn
+++ b/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/BUILD.gn
@@ -1,3 +1,7 @@
 # Copyright 2014 The Chromium Authors
 # Use of this source code is governed by a BSD-style license that can be
 # found in the LICENSE file.
+
+# GHOSTIUM-OVERLAY: pull in the renderer-side FingerprintNoiseSource.
+# Appended to the modules source_set deps: see plan.md section 3.5.
+# Target: //ghostium_src/overlay/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/ghostium_fp
